UID:wrv-2Z04YNC9vOCuvp-C7
SUMMARY:April Business After Hours
DTSTAMP:20260413T004617Z
DTSTART:20260423T003000Z
DESCRIPTION:We're feeling neighborly at April's Business After Hours at The
	 Neighborhood! This Morgan Junction restaurant is built on the promise tha
	t guests should feel as cozy here as they do in their own home. This commu
	nity driven spot focuses on great tasting food and beverages\, exceptional
	 service\, and genuine hospitality\, with an approach rooted in quality\, 
	consistency\, and connection that has earned it a loyal local following al
	ong California Avenue. In person networking is more effective because shar
	ed space and real time interaction increase recall and follow up\, a findi
	ng supported by Harvard Business Review research showing face to face meet
	ings strengthen professional relationships more than digital alternatives.
	 This evening is meant to feel easy and social in the same way the restaur
	ant does\, with room for genuine conversation and connections that make se
	nse locally.  Date and Time Wednesday Apr 22 5:30 PM - 7:30 PM Location 65
	03 California Ave SW Seattle WA 98136\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/even
	ts/#/details/april-business-after-hours/18529091/2026-04-22T00\n\nFrom SEA
	today - Food & Drink
